div></div></div></div><div class="pf-slide"><div style="display:block" class="sc-fHCGaJ cVlURn pf-137_" data-pf-type="SlideshowSlide"><div class="sc-dhKdPU hjOBND pf-136_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-lnPyOc gUmbDa pf-135_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-brPMkR cnEYUf pf-151_ pf-heading-1-h3">Dispose of the shield after use</h3><img title="Expert Advice: Utilising a CPR Face Shield for Optimal Resuscitation - ComplyPlus™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" alt="Expert Advice: Utilising a CPR Face Shield for Optimal Resuscitation - ComplyPlus™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500&width=1200 1200w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_for_Optimal_Resuscitation_-_ComplyPlus_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1728977500&width=1400 1400w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Expert_Advice_Utilising_a_CPR_Face_Shield_f